  <oversight_info>
    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the additive value of tadalafil given together with Diamox (acetazolamide) in
      preventing acute mountain sickness in travelers to high altitude areas.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      A randomized controlled study comparing:

      Tadalafil [20mg x1/day] and acetazolamide [125mg x2 day], versus Acetazolamide [125mg x2 day]
      alone, in trekkers to altitude &gt; 3,000 m.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
